subject: NCAA Basketball Tournament (Men)
Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: The fourth-seeded Terrapins used a 12-2 run early in the second half to glided to an 89-77 victory over No. 13 Houston in the first round of the Midwest Region.
